channel.title: Not yet started server looking for Co-Owner
channel.description:
Title says most of it. I'm looking for someone who will do all of the grunt work on the server. I will give you access to the server via teamviewer and you will mod it how you see fit, with a little input from me. I have a decent server setup, and I will portforward.
Add me on skype if you're interested : christian.scillitoe
